25:[["$","blockquote",null,{"children":["\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"阅读提示\n适合对象：需要排查 Windows 主机异常行为、日志和持久化痕迹的读者。\n阅读前提：会使用事件查看器、任务管理器、注册表和命令行。\n核心收获：建立 Windows 应急排查的优先级和落地命令清单。"}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"当 Windows 服务器或终端出现异常行为时——CPU 飙升、不明外联、文件被篡改——安全人员需要在最短时间内判断系统是否已被入侵，并定位攻击者的活动痕迹。本文将系统讲解 Windows 环境下的应急排查方法，覆盖进程、网络、日志、注册表、计划任务和文件系统六大维度，提供大量可直接执行的排查命令。"}],"\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"windows-安全事件类型","children":["Windows 安全事件类型",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#windows-安全事件类型","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"在开展排查之前，首先需要了解 Windows 环境中常见的安全事件类型："}],"\n",["$","ul",null,{"children":["\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"恶意软件感染"}],"：勒索软件加密文件、挖矿木马占用资源、远控木马（RAT）建立持久化"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"账户安全事件"}],"：暴力破解、凭据窃取（Mimikatz）、横向移动（Pass-the-Hash）"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"权限提升"}],"：利用系统漏洞或配置缺陷从普通用户提权至管理员或 SYSTEM"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"持久化后门"}],"：通过注册表、计划任务、服务、WMI 等机制维持访问权限"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"数据外泄"}],"：敏感文件被压缩外传、数据库被非授权访问导出"]}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"进程排查","children":["进程排查",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#进程排查","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"进程排查是应急响应的第一步。攻击者执行的恶意程序、反弹 Shell、挖矿进程都会以进程形式存在于系统中。"}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"使用-tasklist-排查","children":["使用 tasklist 排查",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#使用-tasklist-排查","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L30","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"使用-wmic-深入排查","children":["使用 WMIC 深入排查",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#使用-wmic-深入排查","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L31","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"使用-powershell-高级排查","children":["使用 PowerShell 高级排查",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#使用-powershell-高级排查","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L32","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"process-explorer-使用要点","children":["Process Explorer 使用要点",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#process-explorer-使用要点","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"Sysinternals Process Explorer 是 Windows 进程排查的利器："}],"\n",["$","ul",null,{"children":["\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"验证签名"}],"：Options → Verify Image Signatures，未签名的进程用红色高亮"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"查看 VirusTotal 检测"}],"：Options → Check VirusTotal.com，直接查询进程文件的恶意检测率"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"父子进程关系"}],"：树形视图直观展示进程层级，识别异常的父子关系（如 Word 启动了 cmd.exe）"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"查看 TCP/IP 连接"}],"：双击进程 → TCP/IP 标签页，查看进程的网络活动"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"DLL 注入检测"}],"：查看进程加载的 DLL 列表，识别异常注入的模块"]}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"网络连接排查","children":["网络连接排查",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#网络连接排查","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"恶意程序通常需要与 C2（Command & Control）服务器通信，因此网络连接排查是发现入侵的重要手段。"}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"使用-netstat-排查","children":["使用 netstat 排查",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#使用-netstat-排查","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L33","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"使用-powershell-网络排查","children":["使用 PowerShell 网络排查",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#使用-powershell-网络排查","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L34","\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"系统日志分析","children":["系统日志分析",["$","a",null,{"cl